===Former Overnight Express services===
Until the opening of the [[Hokkaido Shinkansen]], the following sleeping car services operated;
; ''[[Hokutosei]]'', ''[[Cassiopeia (train)|Cassiopeia]]'': {{STN|Ueno|x}} - (Goryōkaku) - Hakodate - Oshamambe - Higashi-Muroran - (Shiroishi) - Sapporo
; ''[[Twilight Express]]'': {{STN|Osaka|x}} - (Goryōkaku) - Oshamambe - Higashi-Muroran - (Shiroishi) - Sapporo
; ''[[Hamanasu (train)|Hamanasu]]'': {{STN|Aomori|x}} - (Goryōkaku) - Hakodate - Oshamambe - Higashi-Muroran - (Shiroishi) - Sapporo

